578
00:34:16,719 --> 00:34:17,320
Clean it up.

579
00:34:19,360 --> 00:34:20,760
I have no one to support me.

580
00:34:21,199 --> 00:34:22,439
I dare not be arrogant.

581
00:34:23,399 --> 00:34:25,199
I can't compete with Miss Fang,

582
00:34:25,439 --> 00:34:27,399
who is in a big hurry to get married to a eunuch.

583
00:34:27,399 --> 00:34:29,520
You are about to climb higher in higher status.

584
00:34:30,120 --> 00:34:30,560
You!

585
00:34:34,600 --> 00:34:35,760
You've gone too far!

586
00:34:37,399 --> 00:34:38,560
Look at you.

587
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:40,679
I got your sore point?

588
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:44,120
I'll wrestle you to the ground.

589
00:34:44,600 --> 00:34:45,560
Xuelu, take it.

590
00:34:46,199 --> 00:34:46,600
Let go.

591
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:48,560
Don't take that.

592
00:34:48,679 --> 00:34:49,399
You can't take that.

593
00:34:49,719 --> 00:34:50,520
You really can't take that.

594
00:34:55,199 --> 00:34:56,040
Don't waste it.

595
00:34:56,479 --> 00:34:57,239
You can't take that.

596
00:34:57,639 --> 00:34:58,320
Stop fighting!

597
00:35:02,399 --> 00:35:03,040
Manager Fang.

598
00:35:04,360 --> 00:35:04,840
Manager Fang.

599
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:05,719
Manager Fang.

600
00:35:06,399 --> 00:35:07,239
Don't take that.

601
00:35:09,280 --> 00:35:09,760
You!

602
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:11,080
Come over here.

603
00:35:11,879 --> 00:35:12,520
Stay there.

604
00:35:14,560 --> 00:35:15,280
Stop.

605
00:35:15,719 --> 00:35:16,439
I hit you.

606
00:35:18,239 --> 00:35:18,719
Ziping.

607
00:35:19,320 --> 00:35:19,719
Yin Ziping.

608
00:35:19,719 --> 00:35:20,439
Don't take that!

609
00:35:20,439 --> 00:35:21,199
Stop fighting!

610
00:35:23,280 --> 00:35:24,040
Stop fighting!

611
00:35:25,080 --> 00:35:25,800
Don't take it!

612
00:35:25,840 --> 00:35:26,760
Stop fighting!

613
00:35:26,919 --> 00:35:27,439
Ziping!

614
00:35:28,080 --> 00:35:28,520
Ziping!

615
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:30,360
Stop!

616
00:35:32,159 --> 00:35:33,080
The matron is here!

617
00:35:33,679 --> 00:35:34,040
All of you, stop!

618
00:35:37,199 --> 00:35:37,840
Kneel.

619
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:40,919
Kneel for two hours

620
00:35:41,239 --> 00:35:42,159
and reflect on your mistakes.

621
00:35:51,360 --> 00:35:51,879
I...

622
00:35:51,879 --> 00:35:52,479
Kneel properly.

623
00:35:58,520 --> 00:35:59,439
Pretentious.

624
00:36:00,520 --> 00:36:01,199
What about you?

625
00:36:01,639 --> 00:36:02,360
Why did you fight?

626
00:36:16,199 --> 00:36:17,479
His Majesty gave the valuable advice

627
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:19,239
to reinstate Meng.

628
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:22,159
I can't go against his wish.

629
00:36:23,120 --> 00:36:23,959
She seeks gains

630
00:36:24,239 --> 00:36:25,040
in exchange for love.

631
00:36:25,879 --> 00:36:28,399
The head of the Imperial Food Service

632
00:36:28,840 --> 00:36:30,760
must convince everyone.

633
00:36:31,199 --> 00:36:31,800
Otherwise,

634
00:36:32,159 --> 00:36:33,439
even if I give an edict,

635
00:36:33,679 --> 00:36:34,560
you still cannot convince everyone.

636
00:36:36,239 --> 00:36:36,800
Your Majesty,

637
00:36:37,399 --> 00:36:38,479
I have confidence.

638
00:36:40,959 --> 00:36:41,679
In terms of seniority,

639
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:43,600
Meng is far above you.

640
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:47,000
I will let you compete on an equal footing.

641
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:53,760
Your Majesty.

642
00:36:54,439 --> 00:36:55,040
Leave.

643
00:37:02,719 --> 00:37:03,360
Your Majesty,

644
00:37:03,879 --> 00:37:04,919
His Majesty just conferred

645
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:08,080
Guo Xuan, Noble Consort Guo's elder brother,
the title of the Marquis of Wuding.

646
00:37:08,560 --> 00:37:10,840
An exemption was made to confer her grandmother, Yan,
as the Mistress of the Duke of Ying.

647
00:37:11,159 --> 00:37:12,840
Her mother, Xu, was given the title of Lady.

648
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:13,919
Also,

649
00:37:18,159 --> 00:37:20,159
Huang Yan, the Late Emperor's close attendant,
had illicit affairs with foreign ministers

650
00:37:20,600 --> 00:37:21,639
and was executed.

651
00:37:21,840 --> 00:37:23,760
His property and money go to
the Marquis of Wuding.

652
00:37:26,520 --> 00:37:28,439
One should plan first and act later.

653
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:31,040
An impetuous person

654
00:37:31,919 --> 00:37:33,320
cannot achieve great success.

655
00:37:35,840 --> 00:37:36,360
Yes.

656
00:37:43,040 --> 00:37:46,399
(To Grandmother,
from your granddaughter Guo Duansu.)

657
00:37:47,399 --> 00:37:48,639
(After I bade goodbye to you,)

658
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:50,520
(summers and autumns have passed.)

659
00:37:51,080 --> 00:37:53,439
(I heard that you are unwell)

660
00:37:53,679 --> 00:37:55,679
(and sent a eunuch
to bring along an imperial physician)

661
00:37:56,360 --> 00:37:57,560
(to ask about your condition.)

662
00:38:02,720 --> 00:38:04,925
[To the Mistress of the Duke of Ying]

663
00:38:06,399 --> 00:38:06,879
Yujing,

664
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:09,399
make sure you give this letter

665
00:38:09,399 --> 00:38:11,000
to my grandmother personally

666
00:38:11,439 --> 00:38:12,520
and send my message to her.

667
00:38:14,560 --> 00:38:15,639
The company one keeps

668
00:38:15,919 --> 00:38:16,840
has a bearing on his success.

669
00:38:18,080 --> 00:38:19,159
Be respectful and modest,

670
00:38:19,639 --> 00:38:20,639
and you'll safeguard
our forefathers' achievements.

671
00:38:22,159 --> 00:38:24,679
Grandmother, take care of the brothers,
sons, and nephews in the clan,

672
00:38:25,239 --> 00:38:26,560
and the Guo family will be assured

673
00:38:27,280 --> 00:38:28,760
of long-term peace and prosperity.

674
00:38:29,399 --> 00:38:30,040
Your Highness,

675
00:38:30,399 --> 00:38:32,399
now your brother is the marquis,

676
00:38:32,879 --> 00:38:34,879
it is clear that His Majesty favors
the Guo family.

677
00:38:35,399 --> 00:38:37,560
Even Her Majesty's parental home
cannot compare with you.

678
00:38:38,679 --> 00:38:39,879
You should be happy.

679
00:38:40,439 --> 00:38:42,760
Why are you so worried?

680
00:38:43,560 --> 00:38:44,280
When I'm happy,

681
00:38:45,679 --> 00:38:46,919
someone will be unhappy.

682
00:38:48,679 --> 00:38:49,879
I must have a sense of crisis,

683
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:51,280
or

684
00:38:51,879 --> 00:38:52,719
there'll be trouble.

685
00:38:53,600 --> 00:38:54,199
Yes.

686
00:38:55,439 --> 00:38:56,040
Wait.

687
00:39:05,600 --> 00:39:06,120
These are

688
00:39:07,040 --> 00:39:10,000
His Majesty's gift of 1,000-year-old wild ginseng
and 1,000-year-old glossy ganoderma.

689
00:39:11,439 --> 00:39:13,159
This medicine
is from the Imperial Academy of Medicine.

690
00:39:13,560 --> 00:39:14,879
My grandmother is old,

691
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:16,719
frail, and sickly. She catches a cold easily.

692
00:39:17,639 --> 00:39:19,399
This is specially prepared
by the imperial physicians.

693
00:39:19,760 --> 00:39:20,520
Take them.

694
00:39:21,360 --> 00:39:23,840
Watch the maids who are serving my grandmother.

695
00:39:24,239 --> 00:39:25,399
If they neglect her,

696
00:39:25,840 --> 00:39:26,800
dismiss them immediately.

697
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:27,760
Yes.

698
00:39:33,800 --> 00:39:34,520
Stay safe.

699
00:40:01,199 --> 00:40:01,760
Let's go.

700
00:40:24,919 --> 00:40:25,800
Your Highness, you're back.

701
00:40:26,919 --> 00:40:27,639
Why are you here?

702
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:32,879
Didn't you love the Duyou Guqin?

703
00:40:33,760 --> 00:40:34,679
What a pity

704
00:40:34,679 --> 00:40:35,600
that the string is broken.

705
00:40:36,520 --> 00:40:37,280
I found

706
00:40:37,280 --> 00:40:39,000
a string that matches the original guqin

707
00:40:39,360 --> 00:40:40,639
and replaced the broken string.

708
00:40:41,439 --> 00:40:42,040
Listen.

709
00:40:43,040 --> 00:40:45,080
The sound is as clear and smooth as before.

710
00:40:47,760 --> 00:40:49,399
Can I play a song for you

711
00:40:49,719 --> 00:40:50,600
to relieve your boredom?

712
00:40:50,919 --> 00:40:51,560
Don't bother.

713
00:41:05,520 --> 00:41:06,520
Someone will tidy that up.

714
00:41:18,879 --> 00:41:20,360
Your Highness, can you tell me

715
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:22,080
what is troubling you?

716
00:41:22,959 --> 00:41:23,800
I am stupid

717
00:41:24,639 --> 00:41:25,959
and may not be able to resolve your worries

718
00:41:26,760 --> 00:41:28,159
but if you speak your mind,

719
00:41:28,479 --> 00:41:29,760
I will lend you my ears.

720
00:41:30,560 --> 00:41:31,879
-Your Highness.
-Leave the guqin here.

721
00:41:33,760 --> 00:41:34,520
Thank you for your concern.

722
00:41:35,879 --> 00:41:36,600
If there is nothing else,

723
00:41:37,199 --> 00:41:38,040
I'll visit you another day.

724
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:49,479
Your Highness.

725
00:41:51,040 --> 00:41:51,719
Anything else?

726
00:41:52,439 --> 00:41:53,320
This study is simple.

727
00:41:53,560 --> 00:41:54,679
It is unsuitable for a long stay.

728
00:41:55,439 --> 00:41:57,120
Mother fears that the attendants
will neglect you

729
00:41:57,639 --> 00:41:59,080
and sent me here to discuss with you

730
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:00,360
about moving back.

731
00:42:01,080 --> 00:42:02,320
People come and go to the palace every day.

732
00:42:02,320 --> 00:42:03,000
It is very noisy.

733
00:42:03,679 --> 00:42:04,520
This place is elegant

734
00:42:04,879 --> 00:42:05,719
in comparison.

735
00:42:06,360 --> 00:42:07,080
I'll live here.

736
00:42:08,560 --> 00:42:09,439
Your Highness, I should stay

737
00:42:09,439 --> 00:42:10,280
with you then.

738
00:42:11,080 --> 00:42:12,159
If you refuse to move,

739
00:42:12,520 --> 00:42:13,360
from tomorrow onwards,

740
00:42:13,719 --> 00:42:15,000
I'll accompany you more often.

741
00:42:16,399 --> 00:42:17,280
When you are busy,

742
00:42:17,600 --> 00:42:18,679
I'll grind ink and pour tea.

743
00:42:19,360 --> 00:42:20,120
When you are free,

744
00:42:20,520 --> 00:42:21,679
we'll chat so that you're not bored.

745
00:42:22,199 --> 00:42:22,760
Is that fine with you?

746
00:42:23,360 --> 00:42:24,120
I already said

747
00:42:24,560 --> 00:42:25,879
don't serve me day and night.

748
00:42:26,719 --> 00:42:28,479
When Mother was the consort
of the Eastern Palace,

749
00:42:28,800 --> 00:42:30,199
she attended to His Majesty's

750
00:42:30,600 --> 00:42:31,679
daily needs.

751
00:42:32,399 --> 00:42:34,120
This is the duty of a wife.

752
00:42:34,959 --> 00:42:36,320
In the past, Your Highness' tolerance

753
00:42:36,639 --> 00:42:37,639
had made me lazy.

754
00:42:38,120 --> 00:42:39,399
I am seriously changing now.

755
00:42:39,879 --> 00:42:41,040
I said no.

756
00:42:41,560 --> 00:42:42,120
Yuan Qi,

757
00:42:44,280 --> 00:42:45,239
send the Crown Princess back.

758
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:46,280
Yes.

759
00:42:47,040 --> 00:42:47,600
Your Highness,

760
00:42:47,959 --> 00:42:48,520
please.

761
00:42:51,439 --> 00:42:52,719
I will come again tomorrow.

762
00:42:58,959 --> 00:42:59,719
Don't see me off.

763
00:42:59,840 --> 00:43:00,840
Take care of His Highness.

764
00:43:11,879 --> 00:43:12,320
Your Highness,

765
00:43:13,239 --> 00:43:13,919
did you see that?

766
00:43:17,120 --> 00:43:17,919
Why do I feel

767
00:43:18,719 --> 00:43:19,840
that the Crown Princess

768
00:43:20,199 --> 00:43:21,280
is different from the past?

769
00:43:24,760 --> 00:43:25,639
What time is it?

770
00:43:25,919 --> 00:43:26,919
Why hasn't my meal arrived?

771
00:43:27,439 --> 00:43:28,120
It was delivered

772
00:43:28,600 --> 00:43:29,600
earlier.

773
00:43:30,000 --> 00:43:31,120
Miss Yao put the food box

774
00:43:31,120 --> 00:43:32,040
outside.

775
00:43:32,320 --> 00:43:33,800
The Crown Princess was here just now.

776
00:43:39,239 --> 00:43:40,040
She can't just deliver.

777
00:43:40,959 --> 00:43:41,600
Tell her

778
00:43:42,360 --> 00:43:43,800
that I don't like today's meal.

779
00:43:44,159 --> 00:43:44,840
Tell her to make another set.

780
00:43:46,560 --> 00:43:47,199
Again?

781
00:43:50,360 --> 00:43:50,879
Yes.
